examples.en: Sales decreased by five percent this year.
Average house prices decreased by 13% last year.
By 1881, the population of Ireland had decreased to 5.2 million.
The amount of homework decreased towards the end of the semester.
With the passage of time, the number of children suffering with the disease has decreased dramatically.
Butter sales have fallen because margarine has improved in flavor. Further, butter consumption has decreased because of links to heart disease.
